a lawsuit against the lender,

24:03.900 --> 24:05.485
the man is murdered
by a low-level yakuza?

24:08.864 --> 24:10.740
- We've been
down this road before.

24:11.366 --> 24:11.992
Or don't you remember?

24:12.075 --> 24:16.288
- Ohara-san, this is different.

24:16.371 --> 24:17.747
- Sure.

24:17.831 --> 24:18.498
The difference is this case

24:18.582 --> 24:21.334
has a deposition,
a murder weapon,

24:21.418 --> 24:23.545
and a violent criminal
behind bars.

24:23.628 --> 24:23.962
It's closed.

24:38.310 --> 24:40.979
- Cream. Too much sugar.

24:41.062 --> 24:42.522
How you like it.

24:44.232 --> 24:45.317
Thanks.

24:46.484 --> 24:48.653
- Don't take it personal.

24:48.737 --> 24:49.446
He's just...

24:49.529 --> 24:52.115
Racist nationalist.

24:54.117 --> 24:56.119
You've got those too, right?

24:58.288 --> 25:01.750
