25:01.833 --> 25:03.543
You could be living
in Missouri.

25:04.252 --> 25:07.714
That's true.

25:07.797 --> 25:08.715
- Move.

25:08.798 --> 25:09.841
- Sorry.

25:12.636 --> 25:14.262
- Get a solid story

25:14.346 --> 25:15.388
in the paper,
or this is your last paycheck.

25:25.106 --> 25:27.234
- It does have armadillo on it.

25:27.317 --> 25:32.197
I think armadillo looks stupid,
but it's Hasegawa's favorite.

25:32.280 --> 25:33.240
He says it's only animal
with armor,

25:33.323 --> 25:36.201
so it's like samurai
of animal world.

25:39.829 --> 25:41.289
Oh, I'm sorry. Am I boring you?

25:41.373 --> 25:43.625
- No, I'm fascinated
by armadillos.

25:45.794 --> 25:48.296
- I know, I know.
But it looks expensive, right?

25:48.380 --> 25:50.090
I cannot afford more than this.

25:50.173 --> 25:51.258
- Why is that?

25:53.301 --> 25:55.845
- What? What?
Should I be like you?

25:55.929 --> 25:57.639
Save everything
and have no fucking fun?

25:57.722 --> 26:00.475
- Look, if you want to blow
your money on Akira,

26:00.558 --> 26:02.185
that's your business.

26:06.189 --> 26:07.691
- Something's wrong.
What's wrong?

26:11.861 --> 26:13.488
- It's nothing.
I'm tired.

26:16.408 --> 26:18.743
- All right,
I'm going to get this.

27:07.334 --> 27:09.210
- Yeah. You heard me.

27:09.294 --> 27:11.296
I said shut up.

27:11.379 --> 27:14.674
What part of that
don't you understand?

27:14.758 --> 27:16.217
Shut the fuck up! Right now!

27:18.136 --> 27:21.473
- No...no...don't you...
don't you look at me!

